{
  "name": "ai-universal-clipboard",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "This project is a Chrome extension that is a clipboard app, allowing users to save and manage \"clips\" of text and images. The extension relies on a side panel UI, which can be used for listing, adding, and deleting clips. The user data is stored in the browser's local storage.",
